  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CLAIRVOYANCE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Clairvoyance</strong> is a 2D tactical martial arts roguelike inspired by 2000s era flash games and media.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SEIZE YOUR AGENCY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Who are you?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a test subject in a world where human life is secondary to scientific progress. You were designed to be trained, studied, and disposed of.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You need to get out.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hopelessly outnumbered, outgunned, and underprepared, you have but one advantage: you know their next move before they even think of it. This, they could not have planned for. It's time to live or die as a person, not a data point.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>It's time to express yourself.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REALISTIC COMBAT, SUPERNATURAL POWER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clairvoyance features a grounded combat system inspired by real sparring. Footwork affects attack timing. Rolling with a punch can reduce damage. Different types of strikes have unique levels of damage, reach, and risk.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This level of detail would be overwhelming in a traditional brawler. But in Clairvoyance, you're given foresight: a brief glimpse of where attacks will land before they happen. Reaction speed becomes secondary to positioning, precision, and timing with the knowledge of what's coming.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/0655178ee772a21d5523a5620e9469b3.poster.avif?t=1774176550\" width=402 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/0655178ee772a21d5523a5620e9469b3.webm?t=1774176550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/0655178ee772a21d5523a5620e9469b3.mp4?t=1774176550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FREEDOM OF MOVEMENT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forget rigid animations and simplistic hitboxes. In Clairvoyance, you're in control:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tight hitboxes on every limb</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully independent head movement</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mid-attack micro-positioning</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combined, you can bob and weave around attacks like never before while simultaneously preparing your counterattack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/ccc05af62804daddd6464106dc64024c.poster.avif?t=1774176550\" width=546 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/ccc05af62804daddd6464106dc64024c.webm?t=1774176550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/ccc05af62804daddd6464106dc64024c.mp4?t=1774176550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NATURALLY FLOWING ATTACKS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every move has a start stance and an end stance. With this physical logic in combo creation and execution, make use of the natural levels of \"friction\" in using one move after another.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/faa2c7ad174ebf6ec1741bec58ddbdf7.poster.avif?t=1774176550\" width=332 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/faa2c7ad174ebf6ec1741bec58ddbdf7.webm?t=1774176550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/faa2c7ad174ebf6ec1741bec58ddbdf7.mp4?t=1774176550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INSPIRED FIGHTING STYLES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can choose between a variety of fighting styles, each with unique movesets and passives inspired by their real life combat philosophies. The style you choose will define your approach to every fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/e84863c8370c6ca73e645d0636517b69.poster.avif?t=1774176550\" width=598 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/e84863c8370c6ca73e645d0636517b69.webm?t=1774176550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/e84863c8370c6ca73e645d0636517b69.mp4?t=1774176550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ENDLESS POSSIBILITIES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Highly customizable movesets</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Multiple weapon types</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Multiple characters, all with unique stats</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Powerful upgrades and items</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/3c1c9d1b4924c6835b149d3a9019b3cf.poster.avif?t=1774176550\" width=624 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/3c1c9d1b4924c6835b149d3a9019b3cf.webm?t=1774176550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/3c1c9d1b4924c6835b149d3a9019b3cf.mp4?t=1774176550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CLAIRVOYANCE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Clairvoyance</strong> is a 2D tactical martial arts roguelike inspired by 2000s era flash games and media.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SEIZE YOUR AGENCY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Who are you?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a test subject in a world where human life is secondary to scientific progress. You were designed to be trained, studied, and disposed of.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You need to get out.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hopelessly outnumbered, outgunned, and underprepared, you have but one advantage: you know their next move before they even think of it. This, they could not have planned for. It's time to live or die as a person, not a data point.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>It's time to express yourself.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REALISTIC COMBAT, SUPERNATURAL POWER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clairvoyance features a grounded combat system inspired by real sparring. Footwork affects attack timing. Rolling with a punch can reduce damage. Different types of strikes have unique levels of damage, reach, and risk.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This level of detail would be overwhelming in a traditional brawler. But in Clairvoyance, you're given foresight: a brief glimpse of where attacks will land before they happen. Reaction speed becomes secondary to positioning, precision, and timing with the knowledge of what's coming.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/0655178ee772a21d5523a5620e9469b3.poster.avif?t=1774176550\" width=402 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/0655178ee772a21d5523a5620e9469b3.webm?t=1774176550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/0655178ee772a21d5523a5620e9469b3.mp4?t=1774176550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FREEDOM OF MOVEMENT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forget rigid animations and simplistic hitboxes. In Clairvoyance, you're in control:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tight hitboxes on every limb</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully independent head movement</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mid-attack micro-positioning</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combined, you can bob and weave around attacks like never before while simultaneously preparing your counterattack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/ccc05af62804daddd6464106dc64024c.poster.avif?t=1774176550\" width=546 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/ccc05af62804daddd6464106dc64024c.webm?t=1774176550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/ccc05af62804daddd6464106dc64024c.mp4?t=1774176550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NATURALLY FLOWING ATTACKS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every move has a start stance and an end stance. With this physical logic in combo creation and execution, make use of the natural levels of \"friction\" in using one move after another.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/faa2c7ad174ebf6ec1741bec58ddbdf7.poster.avif?t=1774176550\" width=332 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/faa2c7ad174ebf6ec1741bec58ddbdf7.webm?t=1774176550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/faa2c7ad174ebf6ec1741bec58ddbdf7.mp4?t=1774176550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INSPIRED FIGHTING STYLES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can choose between a variety of fighting styles, each with unique movesets and passives inspired by their real life combat philosophies. The style you choose will define your approach to every fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/e84863c8370c6ca73e645d0636517b69.poster.avif?t=1774176550\" width=598 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/e84863c8370c6ca73e645d0636517b69.webm?t=1774176550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/e84863c8370c6ca73e645d0636517b69.mp4?t=1774176550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ENDLESS POSSIBILITIES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Highly customizable movesets</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Multiple weapon types</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Multiple characters, all with unique stats</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Powerful upgrades and items</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/3c1c9d1b4924c6835b149d3a9019b3cf.poster.avif?t=1774176550\" width=624 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113640/extras/3c1c9d1b4924c6835b149d3a9019b3cf.webm?t=1774176550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><s